    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/206b39fbe7ffce175ccb946e50dfb20b.poster.avif?t=1563852035\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/206b39fbe7ffce175ccb946e50dfb20b.webm?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/206b39fbe7ffce175ccb946e50dfb20b.mp4?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备好受苦了吗？那么，欢迎来到《光之迷城》</h2><br><br>一张年代久远的藏宝图，把捷斯引到了这座古堡之前。虽然说是古堡，但周围尽是残垣断壁，其实和废墟没什么两样。眼前的入口覆着一丛残枝败柳，抬头仰望，古堡顶端的房间却闪着耀眼的光芒，两者结合散发着令人无发理解的气息……<br><br>等待捷斯的注定不是一场平凡的探险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/8e3da3cc89d9396853e163771b6be0b2.poster.avif?t=1563852035\" width=616 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/8e3da3cc89d9396853e163771b6be0b2.webm?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/8e3da3cc89d9396853e163771b6be0b2.mp4?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>仔细探索地图每一个角落，发掘城堡的秘密，收集前行的必备道具；<br></li><li>前进的路上难免会有阻滞，用你熟练得令人心痛的操作击败面前的怪物吧；<br></li><li>宝箱藏匿城堡的各处，要正确解读路上发现的提示才能找到它们。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/d13e87a4093cd66c31da0aafe8f8604c.poster.avif?t=1563852035\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/d13e87a4093cd66c31da0aafe8f8604c.webm?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/d13e87a4093cd66c31da0aafe8f8604c.mp4?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特的地图设计，迂回曲折的道路，鼓励玩家探索、收集；<br></li><li>光线、物理、动作、拼图、迷宫、数字...各种类型的谜题等你挑战；<br></li><li>你的武器功能并不单一，巧妙利用它破解机关，穿越障碍；</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/e7cc475ffb576b4e1b41bd56ef577323.poster.avif?t=1563852035\" width=616 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/e7cc475ffb576b4e1b41bd56ef577323.webm?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/e7cc475ffb576b4e1b41bd56ef577323.mp4?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者寄语</h2><br><br>各位玩家好，很荣幸给诸位带来《光之迷城》。这是我们工作室三人合作的第一款作品，也是我们制作的第一款游戏。<br><br>作为《恶魔城》系列的忠实玩家，我自然也希望在这款游戏中融入《恶魔城》的元素。因此，大家在游戏中能看到不少收集要素，而为了鼓励大家进行探索，我们也在设计地图的时候做了一些小捷径，方便大家快速到达想去的地方。<br><br>由于开发经验和资金不足带来的开发期受限，很多想法最终没能实现。但这不意味着我们会放弃这些计划，假以时日，我们希望能实现这些设想，给大家带来更优秀的作品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/c35338f3a915bc3db8395a8c98daa732.poster.avif?t=1563852035\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/c35338f3a915bc3db8395a8c98daa732.webm?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1018170/extras/c35338f3a915bc3db8395a8c98daa732.mp4?t=1563852035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
